"Here is your requested Python coding question:\n\n{\n\"title\": \"Medium: Maximum Sum of Subarray\",\n\"description\": \"Given a list of integers, find the maximum sum of a subarray within that list.\\n\\n#### Function Signature\\n```python\\ndef max_sum_subarray(arr: list[int]) -> int:\\n```\\n\\n#### Input\\n- `arr` (list[int]): A list of integers.\\n\\n#### Output\\n- Returns the maximum sum of a subarray within the input list.\\n\",\n\"code\": \"\"\"\ndef max_sum_subarray(arr: list[int]) -> int:\n    if not arr:\n        return 0\n\n    max_sum = float('-inf')\n    current_sum = 0\n\n    for num in arr:\n        current_sum = max(num, current_sum + num)\n        max_sum = max(max_sum, current_sum)\n\n    return max_sum\n\"\"\",\n\"tests\": [\n\"assert max_sum_subarray([-2,1,-3,4,-1,2,1,-5,4]) == 6\",\n\"assert max_sum_subarray([1, -2, 3, 10, -4, 7, 2, -5]) == 12\",\n\"assert max_sum_subarray([-1, -2, -3, -4, -5]) == -1\"\n]\n}"